2026-05-10T04:51:30.3970702Z 13    <!--
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4031554Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4032608Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
