2026-05-10T04:51:30.4041515Z 22    <!--
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4042098Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4042835Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4043520Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4044348Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4045184Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4046004Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4046818Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4047676Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4048501Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4049279Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-10T04:51:30.4049887Z 33    -->
