2026-05-10T04:51:30.9027037Z 12    <!--
2026-05-10T04:51:30.9027441Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T04:51:30.9027816Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
